# Coordinator Python

- FastAPI routes in `coordinator/src/main.py`; classify public / node / operator.
- Operator mutations: `_require_operator` + `X-Operator-Key`.
- Size-limit large JSON with `_require_json_size` before persisting.
- Persist with atomic tmp+replace and locks where concurrent (see `StateStore`, `JobQueue`).
- Do not `importlib` / `eval` / `exec` network-supplied code on the coordinator.
- Local launcher (`ENABLE_LOCAL_LAUNCHER`) is single-tenant ops only; keep default off in library code.
- Prefer typed Pydantic models; avoid unstructured dicts for new APIs.
